Description: Async client for AWS services using botocore and aiohttp (Avalan PPA transitive)
 aiobotocore wraps botocore so that the AWS service clients can be
 driven from asyncio code without blocking the event loop. This
 package is built for the Avalan PPA because aioboto3 15.5.0
 (Avalan's `vendors` extra) `==`-pins aiobotocore at 2.25.1 and
 Noble's archive does not carry it.
